OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FDowning Street has resisted
OL,7,Fimmediately sacking an immigration
OL,8,Fminister after Shabana Mahmood asked
OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer to fire him for
OL,10,Fallegedly breaching the ministerial
OL,11,Fcode.
OL,13,FThe Home Secretary had called for the
OL,14,FPrime Minister to dismiss Mike Tapp
OL,15,Fafter he wrote an article suggesting
OL,16,Fforeign care workers should be exempt
OL,17,Ffrom her plans to tighten settlement
OL,18,Frules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
