PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782434875
OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FBut there appeared to be a stand-off
OL,7,Fon Thursday evening as No 10 said the
OL,8,FHome Office minister remained in post
OL,9,Fand it is understood a decision has
OL,10,Fnot yet been made by Sir Keir.
OL,12,FIn an article for The Times, Mr Tapp
OL,13,Fsaid his "strong belief" was that
OL,14,Fthose already working in the UK care
OL,15,Fsystem should not have to wait longer
OL,16,Fto qualify for indefinite leave to
OL,17,Fremain (ILR).
OL,26,@uD@JOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
