OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FThe Home Office minister reportedly
OL,7,Fwrote that he had been working closely
OL,8,Fwith officials to "develop a better
OL,9,Fapproach than a blanket retrospective
OL,10,Fextension from five years to 10 years
OL,11,Ffor everyone".
OL,13,FHome Secretary Ms Mahmood has proposed
OL,14,Fto double the time it takes for most
OL,15,Fmigrants to qualify for permanent
OL,16,Fresidence to a decade, including for
OL,17,Fclaimants who are already in the UK
OL,18,Fbut have not yet received ILR.
OL,26,@pD@SOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
