OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FA Government source said on Thursday:
OL,7,F"The Home Secretary has asked the
OL,8,FPrime Minister for Mike Tapp to be
OL,9,Fsacked for breaching the ministerial
OL,10,Fcode."
OL,12,FThey suggested he had broken
OL,13,Fcollective responsibility, a
OL,14,Fconvention whereby individual
OL,15,Fministers speak publicly for the
OL,16,FGovernment as a whole, by writing an
OL,17,Farticle which was out of step with
OL,18,FHome Office policy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
