OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782434875
OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary is said to have
OL,7,Fbeen unaware of the piece and believes
OL,8,Fthe Dover and Deal MP should be
OL,9,Fdismissed from his role as minister
OL,10,Ffor migration and citizenship.
OL,12,FMr Tapp has been loyal to Sir Keir
OL,13,Feven as his authority drained away
OL,14,Facross the wider Parliamentary Labour
OL,15,FParty and expressed disappointment
OL,16,Fwhen the Prime Minister announced his
OL,17,Fresignation on Monday, calling it a
OL,18,F"sad day".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
