OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FThe questions over his future come
OL,7,Famid broader turmoil at the top of
OL,8,FGovernment, after Andy Burnham emerged
OL,9,Fas the frontrunner to replace the
OL,10,FLabour leader as early as July 17.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, Cabinet ministers backed
OL,13,Fthe former Greater Manchester Mayor,
OL,14,Fwho looks set to enter No 10 within
OL,15,Fweeks unless a challenger launches a
OL,16,Fbid for the top job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
