OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782434875
OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper,
OL,7,FHealth Secretary James Murray and
OL,8,FChancellor Rachel Reeves ` who faces
OL,9,Fthe prospect of losing her Cabinet
OL,10,Frole under a Burnham government ` all
OL,11,Fpublicly endorsed him for the
OL,12,Fleadership.
OL,14,FSir Keir has said he hopes to ensure
OL,15,Fdisruption is "absolutely minimised"
OL,16,Fas he prepares to hand over power and
OL,17,Fpromised to seek a "smooth" transition
OL,18,Fto the next premiership.
OL,26,@wD@OOUwD@dO]yD@TOUyD@[O]
