OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,F"I'm going to be professional, I'm
OL,7,Fgoing to have foremost in my mind a
OL,8,Fsense of service and duty that has
OL,9,Fdriven me as Prime Minister," he told
OL,10,Freporters on Thursday.
OL,12,F"I will continue to faithfully serve
OL,13,Fmy country to make sure that any
OL,14,Fdisruption is absolutely minimised,
OL,15,Fand that's why I'm taking steps now to
OL,16,Fensure that can be done in a sensible
OL,17,Fway."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]tD@AOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
