OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FMr Burnham is expected to begin
OL,7,Fsetting out his policy platform in the
OL,8,Fcoming days, with a speech on the
OL,9,Feconomy pledging growth and committing
OL,10,Fhimself to Labour's existing rules on
OL,11,Fborrowing next week.
OL,13,FThe i Paper reported that one plan
OL,14,Fbeing drawn up was to give regional
OL,15,Fmayors powers to control business
OL,16,Frates in their area. Allies of the MP
OL,17,Fconfirmed he had received advice on
OL,18,Fthis but not that he was necessarily
OL,19,Fminded to do do so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
