OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782434875
OL,3,CMahmood in standoff with No 10 after
OL,4,Ccall to sack junior minister
OL,6,FSome Labour MPs had considered whether
OL,7,Fto endorse another candidate to
OL,8,Fprevent a coronation that would see
OL,9,Fthe former mayor secure the leadership
OL,10,Funopposed, but few potential
OL,11,Fcontenders have emerged.
OL,13,FSenior minister Darren Jones has ruled
OL,14,Fout running, and former defence
OL,15,Fminister Al Carns has not formally
OL,16,Fannounced a leadership bid in a series
OL,17,Fof interviews in recent days despite
OL,18,Fconsidering the prospect of a
OL,19,Fchallenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
